op."],[412,492,"We're not playing this"],[492,592,"fucking song tonight."],[617,692,"The fuck, dude?"],[692,859,"Sharp Objects is our anthem."],[859,934,"What the hell you mean"],[934,996,"you're pulling it?"],[996,1088,"Yeah, Phoenix."],[1121,1184,"Why?"],[1222,1359,"Just leave me the fuck alone,"],[1388,1459,"all of you."],[2310,2394,"Here,"],[2435,2523,"let me help."],[2635,2790,"Hey, you're Lennon,"],[2815,2940,"Phoenix's sober companion."],[3011,3144,"Uh, I'm George."],[3182,3257,"I'm here to replace"],[3257,3461,"the original bassist, Josh."],[3482,3620,"Oh, yeah."],[3620,3753,"He got into a car crash,"],[3753,3853,"it's terrible."],[3853,3933,"Yeah, it's terrible."],[3933,3991,"But you know,"],[3991,4124,"nobody made him do all that coke."],[4333,4441,"George, why do you think"],[4441,4612,"Phoenix started using drugs?"],[4612,4733,"He's always been a fuck-up."],[4833,5038,"If you ask me, I'd say stay the hell away."],[5075,5213,"No, he wasn't always like this,"],[5213,5376,"and I'm hired to help him."],[5492,5759,"Look, you seem really nice, Lennon,"],[5885,6043,"but some people can't be saved,"],[6081,6177,"and you shouldn't let people"],[6177,6318,"like that drag you down."],[6577,6723,"What the fuck is going on?"]],"18":[[0,145,"What the fuck is going on?"],[196,308,"Bro, what do you think?"],[638,779,"Phoenix, man, just chill."],[804,880,"Come on."],[1038,1101,"Touch her again"],[1101,1251,"and I'm gonna break your fucking jaw."],[1317,1455,"Don't worry, you'll still be able to play."],[1626,1718,"You're coming with me."],[2043,2131,"God, Phoenix,"],[2131,2235,"what is the matter with you?"],[2235,2281,"You're welcome."],[2281,2369,"That creep was slobbering"],[2369,2439,"all over you."],[2439,2531,"You know what? He was being nice."],[2531,2619,"Ever heard of that word,"],[2619,2744,"or do I need to spell it out for you?"],[2744,2869,"You like nice guys now?"],[2948,3048,"Yeah, I'm sure he's gonna"],[3048,3174,"fucking write you poetry,"],[3174,3278,"and buy you flowers"],[3278,3382,"until your eyes shine"],[3382,3486,"like the fucking stars."],[3486,3578,"But guess what, Lennon?"],[3699,3862,"Nice guys don't fuck like me."]],"19":[[554,738,"Nice guys don't steal songs either!"],[738,846,"Ten seconds with that asshole"],[846,955,"and you'll be fucking bored, Lennon."],[955,1055,"He's not for you."],[1055,1113,"You need someone"],[1113,1234,"who's gonna challenge you,"],[1259,1401,"show you new things."],[1793,1956,"Oh, you've shown me things, Phoenix."],[2285,2352,"You've shown me"],[2352,2469,"how childish and selfish"],[2469,2581,"a grown-ass man can be!"],[2581,2656,"You know what I think?"],[2656,2781,"I think you'd rather spend all night"],[2781,2848,"arguing with me"],[2848,2932,"than ten seconds in bed"],[2932,3044,"with that fucking nice guy."],[3044,3082,"And what,"],[3082,3153,"so I'm not allowed"],[3153,3340,"to fuck other guys except you?"],[3432,3536,"Well, you sure liked it"],[3536,3678,"when we fucked four years ago."],[3958,4041,"Yeah,"],[4124,4250,"I want it, Phoenix."],[4721,4817,"Come on, Lennon."],[4850,5009,"I know you're dying to fuck me."],[5092,5171,"Just say the word"],[5171,5288,"and I will take you right back"],[5288,5413,"to that night four years ago."]],"20":[[1051,1180,"I don't need you to take me back"],[1180,1284,"to that night, Phoenix."],[1305,1484,"I go back to that night all the time."],[2381,2456,"So let's get real."],[2552,2652,"Question one,"],[2752,2873,"what came first?"],[3003,3219,"Weed, shrooms, molly, coke."],[3261,3382,"What the fuck is this?"],[3428,3520,"Sober training."],[3545,3728,"I am your sober companion, aren't I?"],[3766,3895,"So question two,"],[3937,4029,"when did you start"],[4029,4116,"using drugs and alcohol"],[4116,4212,"to numb yourself?"],[4233,4400,"This is fucking bullshit, I'm leaving."],[4767,4967,"I'm doing my job, Phoenix."],[5092,5234,"We can do this on our own,"],[5267,5422,"or I can leave you chained to the chair."],[5422,5526,"It's your choice."],[5638,5751,"So question three,"],[5805,6026,"why did you start using drugs?"],[6189,6356,"Was it because you realized"],[6356,6523,"that your whole entire career"],[6523,6669,"is based on a stolen song,"],[6719,6886,"and that deep down you're really a fraud?"],[7069,7228,"Or, is it because you know that deep down"],[7228,7303,"you screwed up"],[7303,7490,"and there's nothing that you can ever do"],[7520,7611,"to make it right?"],[7970,8087,"Aren't you tired?"],[8229,8433,"Don't you wanna let it all out?"],[8558,8654,"Well you're in luck,"],[8683,8904,"because I was there when you fucked up."],[9054,9184,"You fucked me up."],[9305,9388,"So go on,"],[9513,9592,"admit it."],[9672,9793,"Admit that you-"],[9793,9951,"I know, I fucking know, Lennon."],[9976,10072,"You think I don't fucking know"],[10072,10155,"that I hurt you?"],[10181,10293,"I fucking think about it"],[10293,10385,"every fucking day."],[10385,10464,"For the last four years"],[10464,10535,"it's haunted me."]],"21":[[8,95,"But I was 18,"],[179,254,"eight-fucking-teen,"],[254,350,"and my dad beat the shit out of me"],[350,400,"my whole life."],[400,533,"And when I saw a chance"],[533,663,"to get out of that hell, I took it,"],[663,717,"remember?"],[717,796,"I showed you."],[796,855,"Bat,"],[1005,1088,"crowbar."],[1234,1343,"Cigs."],[1372,1413,"Yeah."],[1413,1659,"And I tattooed your song over my scars"],[1659,1801,"because your song changed my life."],[1901,2018,"You changed my life."],[2168,2314,"You said you wanna fucking ruin me,"],[2419,2602,"but I can tell Lennon, you still care."],[2831,3023,"I was 18 too, Phoenix."],[3065,3190,"And you got out of your hell"],[3190,3324,"by putting me through mine."],[3324,3386,"I know,"],[3411,3474,"I know,"],[3599,3766,"and I don't expect you to forgive me."],[3895,3983,"But I wish that you would"],[3983,4137,"stop looking at me like you hate me."],[4341,4471,"And I wish I could kiss you"],[4471,4554,"the way I used to,"],[4554,4667,"and you would kiss me back."]],"22":[[1901,1956,"Wait."],[2022,2118,"Phoenix, no, I-"],[2223,2310,"What the fuck?"],[2381,2502,"You're fucking recording me?"],[2602,2698,"No, I was just trying to..."],[2698,2752,"You were what?"],[2752,2902,"Trying to get my fucking confession?"],[2994,3111,"I fucking opened up to you"],[3111,3207,"and you manipulated me."],[3207,3328,"You didn't tell me shit."],[3332,3420,"That's not true."],[3420,3470,"Okay."],[3470,3528,"Question one,"],[3528,3611,"why the fuck did you"],[3611,3703,"drop out of Dartmouth?"],[3795,3899,"Question number two,"],[3916,4091,"why the fuck did you work at a strip club?"],[4429,4500,"Question number three,"],[4500,4583,"why the fuck did you"],[4583,4688,"come back into my life?"],[4996,5096,"That's what I thought."],[5547,5651,"I guess we both have a reason"],[5651,5743,"to hate each other now."]],"23":[[792,921,"Let's hit my room, girls, come on."],[930,1055,"I just rocked that fucking show,"],[1067,1201,"I'm about to rock your fucking night!"],[4850,4917,"Wow."],[4971,5150,"Look who the fuck decided"],[5150,5347,"to invade our little humble party."]],"24":[[75,237,"I'm Phoenix's sober companion."],[237,421,"I need a moment alone with my client."],[454,629,"Are you fucking serious?"],[629,829,"Yeah, who the hell do you think you are?"],[871,1021,"We're not going anywhere."],[1021,1209,"Phoenix doesn't need a sober companion"],[1209,1338,"when he has us,"],[1401,1476,"right, baby?"],[1514,1685,"Look, I know that your frontal cortex"],[1685,1839,"hasn't fully developed yet,"],[1864,1997,"but let me break it down for you."],[2060,2235,"Either you go into that bathroom,"],[2235,2356,"or I call security."],[2356,2456,"Security?"],[2519,2581,"And then you can spend"],[2581,2673,"a cozy night in jail"],[2673,2773,"until mommy and daddy"],[2773,2857,"come to bail you out."],[2857,2952,"So what's it gonna be?"],[3044,3161,"Fine, let's go girls."],[3395,3482,"Bye."],[4204,4304,"Wow."],[4396,4550,"Not gonna lie, that kinda turned me on."],[4888,4967,"I don't give a shit"],[4967,5134,"who you fuck, Phoenix,"],[5155,5388,"but if you slip, it's my head."],[5451,5555,"Alright, so you're just here"],[5555,5668,"working on good merits."],[5697,5847,"And that didn't bother you at all?"],[5939,6110,"No, it doesn't bother me,"],[6110,6210,"not at all."],[6210,6335,"I even have a little something"],[6335,6414,"to prove to you"],[6414,6614,"how little it does bother me."],[6890,6956,"Lennon."],[7198,7261,"You see, Lennon,"],[7261,7394,"now I'm a little offended,"],[7394,7536,"because I know it's been four years,"],[7536,7628,"but large?"],[7749,7882,"You know I'm bigger than that."],[8187,8308,"Do you have any more drugs on you?"],[8475,8550,"I don't know."],[8725,8875,"Why don't you find out for yourself?"],[9234,9426,"Go on, search me."]],"25":[[196,396,"Don't think I won't, Phoenix Walker."],[396,613,"Oh, I'm counting on it, Lennon Michael."],[2364,2510,"Oh, you're enjoying this."],[2623,2744,"Not as much as you."],[3028,3132,"I'm not done yet."],[3499,3561,"Uh uh."],[3674,3753,"Eyes up here."],[5334,5438,"I guess you're clean."],[5522,5622,"I am."],[5805,5960,"You're not fucking leaving me again."]],"26":[[450,729,"What's taking that fat-ass so long?"],[788,934,"She's just jealous."],[934,1096,"Phoenix would never fuck someone"],[1096,1209,"who looks like her."],[1317,1393,"Lennon."],[1509,1564,"No,"],[1605,1768,"go and entertain your guests,"],[1768,1901,"isn't that why you brought them"],[1901,2027,"back to your hotel room?"],[2469,2673,"What was it that you said to them earlier?"],[2727,2894,"Rock their fucking world?"],[2957,3011,"Yeah,"],[3011,3098,"why don't you do that?"],[3745,3812,"Hi."],[3924,4141,"Now that the witch is gone,"],[4141,4437,"it's party time!"],[4804,4871,"Get out."],[4925,4996,"What?"],[5009,5109,"Phoenix,"],[5109,5184,"boo boo."],[5184,5317,"I said, get the fuck out."],[5442,5559,"It's fine, let's go girls."],[7624,7741,"Phoenix."]],"27":[[50,129,"Phoenix."],[1209,1380,"You said you don't want me, Lennon."],[1463,1564,"You lied to me."],[1743,1901,"You're the one who doesn't want me,"],[2006,2143,"go back to your plans."],[2585,2694,"I want one thing,"],[2769,2865,"I want you."],[5860,5997,"I want you to beg."],[6126,6185,"Come on,"],[6339,6514,"lose control with me."],[6669,6740,"We can't,"],[6740,6790,"we shouldn't,"],[6790,6911,"we're not friends, Phoenix."],[6911,7032,"Of course we're not friends,"],[7077,7219,"because friends..."],[7515,7695,"don't turn you on like this."],[7745,7866,"So you're gonna be a good girl"],[7866,7995,"and tell me what I wanna hear?"]],"28":[[95,241,"I want you, Phoenix."],[496,550,"Good."],[2894,2948,"Fuck,"],[3057,3194,"that was just a dream."],[3249,3361,"Josh."],[3386,3490,"No."],[3849,3916,"Fuck."],[4170,4220,"Ready?"],[4233,4291,"What?"],[4295,4337,"More."],[4341,4400,"Ah, shi-"],[4963,5142,"Fucking go, man!"],[5221,5455,"Let's fucking go!"],[5893,5976,"Watch out!"],[6418,6606,"I'm sorry, I'm sorry, this is all my fault."],[6606,6685,"I'm sorry, no,"],[6685,6769,"Josh, no,"],[6769,6869,"please stay with me, please."],[6894,7257,"No, no, fuck!"],[8958,9042,"I'm sorry."],[9234,9317,"Phoenix?"]],"29":[[20,183,"Hey, hey, hey."],[183,221,"It's okay,"],[221,279,"it's okay."],[279,333,"I've got you."],[333,442,"You're just having a bad dream,"],[442,496,"it's okay."],[496,571,"I'm here,"],[679,750,"I'm here."],[771,892,"Calm down, calm down."],[1422,1614,"You're gonna regret that in the morning."],[1630,1730,"How about a soda?"],[1864,2010,"Soda's not gonna help me forget."],[2039,2193,"Neither is getting trashed."],[2356,2485,"Do you want to talk about it?"],[2585,2644,"No,"],[2669,2736,"never."],[2957,3028,"Okay,"],[3073,3136,"um,"],[3240,3374,"I guess I'll talk about it."],[3536,3824,"I know that Josh was your friend,"],[3945,4087,"and that losing him was hard,"],[4237,4421,"and I think that's why you started using."],[4654,4783,"You don't fucking understand."],[4925,5142,"Then help me understand."],[5497,5622,"I was fucking there,"],[5718,5834,"I was in the fucking car."],[5901,6010,"It was my fucking fault."],[6118,6210,"Chandler and the PR team"],[6210,6318,"made it seem like he was alone."],[6318,6468,"But I was in the fucking car, and"],[6468,6610,"I knew that he was too high to drive,"],[6614,6698,"and I was"],[6760,6923,"too fucked up to give a fuck."],[7057,7178,"So I watched my best fucking friend"],[7178,7273,"take his last breath."],[7415,7524,"Hey, come here,"],[7553,7632,"it's okay."],[7891,7957,"It's okay."]],"30":[[300,442,"Just like my fucking dad."],[442,546,"Lennon, I'm a fucking..."],[704,829,"I'm a fucking monster"],[829,917,"and I fuck up everything"],[917,988,"that I touch."],[1005,1055,"No."],[1088,1155,"No, no,"],[1155,1263,"don't say that."],[1455,1572,"No, look at me."],[1609,1743,"I said this four years ago"],[1743,1835,"and I'll say it again."],[1951,2081,"You're nothing like him,"],[2110,2243,"you can never be him."],[2339,2419,"Do you think that,"],[2585,2711,"that Josh would forgive me?"],[3069,3178,"More importantly,"],[3178,3336,"he'd want you to forgive yourself."],[3436,3620,"Everybody makes mistakes, Phoenix."],[3620,3853,"It's what we do after that matters."],[3870,3978,"Easy for you to say,"],[4004,4166,"you've never made a mistake in your life."],[4166,4266,"You have perfect grades,"],[4266,4358,"you're Ivy League."],[4379,4479,"I still remember dropping you off"],[4479,4608,"at your family mansion."],[4608,4696,"Phoenix,"],[4754,4879,"my dad is dying."],[4909,5013,"That's why I got a job"],[5013,5171,"bartending at a strip club."],[5192,5363,"I'm all that he has,"],[5572,5730,"and I won't give up on him."],[5889,5976,"Your band"],[6068,6243,"and your fans, they need you."],[6348,6464,"You can't give up."],[6760,6848,"Hey, Lennon,"],[7223,7407,"will you stay with me"],[7444,7532,"for the night, please?"]],"31":[[191,241,"Please. - I-"],[258,379,"Hey, I'll sleep on the floor,"],[379,446,"you can sleep on the bed."],[446,538,"Just please stay."],[829,884,"Okay."],[942,980,"Okay."],[980,1026,"Just..."],[1134,1222,"scooch."],[2106,2327,"Lennon, I'm really glad"],[2327,2427,"that you came back."]],"32":[[1267,1334,"Coffee?"],[1630,1776,"I still must be dreaming,"],[1776,1851,"Mr. Walker."],[2027,2331,"You might be, Miss Michael,"],[2456,2565,"because"],[2673,2806,"I got you a gift."],[2831,2919,"Last night,"],[2919,3165,"Phoenix finally opened up to me."],[3165,3336,"Has he really changed?"],[3336,3457,"Have we changed?"],[4216,4325,"I know you need the money,"],[4350,4441,"and I've been asking around"],[4441,4571,"and that's a really fair price"],[4571,4700,"for a song like Sharp Objects."],[5238,5480,"You're paying me five hundred grand"],[5480,5659,"for the song that you stole from me?"]],"33":[[41,275,"You're paying me five hundred grand"],[275,454,"for the song that you stole from me?"],[454,583,"I thought that's what you wanted."],[688,850,"God, you're unbelievable!"],[1005,1088,"Lennon, you're not fucking"],[1088,1155,"going anywhere."],[1155,1255,"You're not shutting me out again."],[1267,1476,"You know, I envy you, Phoenix."],[1509,1659,"What's it like to have the guts,"],[1659,1856,"the audacity to waltz to a girl"],[1856,1951,"and pay her five hundred grand"],[1951,2131,"after stealing everything from her?"],[2131,2289,"It was one fucking song, Lennon,"],[2289,2394,"get over it!"],[2506,2577,"Get over it?"],[2677,2952,"Do you have any idea what it's like for me"],[3015,3123,"when I hear that song?"],[3274,3411,"On the radio, at a cafe,"],[3411,3582,"at a fucking karaoke bar."],[3678,3849,"Every time I hear you sing it,"],[3849,3978,"it rips my heart out."],[4141,4300,"Okay, well if I fucking rip your heart out"],[4300,4391,"and you hate me so much,"],[4391,4466,"then I bet you wish"],[4466,4637,"I died in that car crash too, don't you?"],[4721,4788,"You kidding me?"],[4871,4938,"When I saw that"],[4938,5038,"it wasn't you on the news,"],[5038,5188,"I did cry my eyes out."],[5392,5501,"No