 happen to my dad?"],[2248,2385,"that's dying in a hospital bed"],[2385,2494,"right now as we speak?"],[2494,2623,"Listen, we can fix this."],[2623,2694,"We'll figure it out."],[2882,3069,"There's no we, Phoenix."],[3069,3299,"You kiss me, they fire me."],[3349,3545,"You cross the line, they blacklist me."],[3657,3883,"Whatever you do, I pay the price."],[3953,4066,"And you don't give a shit,"],[4195,4320,"because you don't have to."],[4550,4633,"But I do."],[4917,5075,"The moment you stole my song,"],[5142,5267,"we're in two different worlds."],[5430,5513,"You're a star,"],[5643,5751,"and I'm a nobody,"],[5784,5968,"trying to keep my head above water."],[6039,6410,"So please, don't say you love me."],[6468,6606,"Unless you're ready to be the reason"],[6606,6735,"that I lose everything."]],"49":[[241,475,"Tonight is the night, folks."],[492,625,"We've got rock music's"],[625,759,"latest sensation,"],[759,967,"Grammy winner Sharp Objects."],[1017,1263,"So Phoenix, during this tour,"],[1263,1422,"you haven't played your mega-hit"],[1422,1580,"Sharp Objects once."],[1622,1785,"Can you tell your fans why?"],[2110,2193,"Um..."],[2364,2556,"Yeah, Sharp Objects is"],[2573,2681,"and it's always"],[2681,2744,"gonna be the song"],[2744,2890,"that was closest to my heart,"],[3028,3165,"but, um,"],[3311,3465,"I'm never gonna sing it again."],[3774,3824,"Ever."]],"50":[[608,658,"Hey."],[684,850,"Hey, hey, hey, why the fuck"],[850,988,"would he just do that?"],[1105,1251,"Anyone in class would like to"],[1251,1409,"fucking share them right here?"],[1476,1593,"This is a goddamn nightmare,"],[1651,1735,"he's trying to kill the band."],[1735,1935,"He's trying to kill my fucking band!"],[2227,2406,"Phoenix, what the hell was that?"],[2406,2544,"I said I wasn't gonna sing the song"],[2544,2648,"I stole from you anymore."],[2811,2898,"Isn't that the confession"],[2898,2948,"you want?"],[2948,3086,"That wasn't confessing."],[3086,3232,"That was running away!"],[3332,3645,"Look, I know that I was mad"],[3645,3745,"that you stole my song,"],[3766,4149,"but I realized that it gave you a band."],[4175,4262,"It gave you a family"],[4262,4346,"that you've never had,"],[4346,4550,"and I take comfort in that."],[4654,4763,"I told you, Len."],[4825,4971,"You said you wanted to ruin me."],[5084,5226,"Even after everything we've been through,"],[5226,5301,"you're still kind."],[5505,5684,"Fuck you, Phoenix Walker."],[6026,6160,"I can't sing that song, though."],[6335,6473,"Every time I hear it, I think about you."],[6785,6890,"It's your song, not mine."],[7469,7570,"We'll get through this,"],[7657,7761,"I promise."],[7953,8053,"Our band's biggest hit"],[8053,8241,"was stolen from Lennon?"],[8425,8529,"I gotta do something"],[8529,8662,"before this ruins the band."]],"51":[[792,955,"Chandler, what is this?"],[1026,1117,"I packed for you."],[1151,1384,"Because I'm ending your contract early,"],[1384,1555,"you no longer work for the band"],[1555,1643,"or for Phoenix."],[1710,1768,"What?"],[1768,1822,"Why?"],[1851,1976,"I mean, don't worry, I'm still gonna"],[1976,2093,"pay you the full amount."],[2093,2485,"And also, sign that NDA,"],[2552,2677,"you get a million dollars."],[3278,3411,"Copyright transfer?"],[3511,3586,"You know-"],[3586,3728,"I could care less"],[3757,3891,"how or when Phoenix"],[3891,4020,"took your song from you."],[4049,4166,"All I know"],[4204,4362,"is it's now our"],[4362,4542,"motherfucking mega hit,"],[4562,4637,"and we're not just gonna"],[4637,4792,"let it go for nothing."],[4846,5180,"So, sign the paper,"],[5246,5455,"take the money,"],[5526,5618,"and walk away."]],"52":[[20,187,"You never claim rights to the song,"],[225,367,"you never see Phoenix."],[437,496,"Ever"],[538,596,"again,"],[596,696,"thank fucking Christ."],[788,896,"You're paying me off"],[896,1046,"to take my song from me?"],[1046,1126,"Whoa, whoa, whoa."],[1126,1230,"Who's taking what?"],[1230,1380,"I'm not taking anything,"],[1422,1651,"I am buying your song."],[1676,