ike him."],[667,855,"No, Phoenix, you saved me."],[909,1096,"You're not him, you could never be him."],[1505,1614,"You're lucky I'm not you."],[2093,2202,"That's my boy."],[2206,2435,"I knew you couldn't hurt your daddy."],[2435,2531,"He won't,"],[2569,2744,"but we can't make any promises."],[2773,2877,"Come on, Vance,"],[2877,3003,"let's shut down the station."],[3003,3086,"Fuck it, Doug."],[3086,3228,"Come on, come on, come on, guys."],[3228,3324,"Come on."],[3324,3365,"Jeez."],[3403,3499,"Phoenix, come on."],[3520,3591,"Help me out."],[3603,3678,"I'm your old man."],[3678,3782,"Don't let them do this."],[3791,3958,"Rot in fucking jail, Dad."],[4079,4141,"Shit."],[4154,4270,"Okay, I'm going."],[4617,4662,"Lennon,"],[4763,4867,"I'm so sorry."],[4925,5000,"I thought I was too late,"],[5000,5096,"I thought I was gonna lose you."],[5205,5284,"It's never too late,"],[5284,5359,"you're here now"],[5359,5476,"and that's all that matters."],[5593,5647,"We gotta go."],[5647,5793,"I set up a live stream for the band."],[5860,5939,"I'm gonna tell everyone"],[5939,6068,"Sharp Objects is your song,"],[6268,6356,"And you're mine."],[6498,6635,"Okay, but there's someone"],[6635,6756,"that we need to talk to first."],[6911,6965,"Okay."]],"64":[[342,425,"Hey, guys."],[567,884,"So, um, I called you guys here"],[884,992,"because I have to confess"],[992,1309,"that I didn't write Sharp Objects."],[1488,1534,"I know it's our"],[1534,1605,"biggest fucking song,"],[1605,1697,"It's our biggest fucking hit,"],[1697,1922,"but Lennon wrote it"],[2014,2168,"and I stole it from her four years ago."],[2293,2402,"So I set up a live stream"],[2402,2540,"and we're gonna confess to the fans"],[2540,2786,"that I stole it,"],[2836,2973,"and there's gonna be fucking backlash"],[2973,3053,"and it's not just gonna"],[3053,3115,"be pointed at me,"],[3115,3236,"it's gonna be pointed at all of us."],[3269,3386,"And I'm sorry, I'm not trying to"],[3386,3486,"drag you guys down with me,"],[3486,3557,"but I 